description: Functionally strategy +‎ -etic, rendering στρατηγητικός (stratēgētikós), a rare variant of στρατηγικός (stratēgikós) (whence the more common English word strategic).

adjectives.description: strategetic (comparative more strategetic, superlative most strategetic)

examples: The importance of having these great strategetic points fortified has been demonstrated by scientific gentlemen conversant with these subjects.
